to make the move.

59
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:35,632
Waiting?
So, what? That was your first kiss?

60
00:03:36,382 --> 00:03:39,010
No, it was two nights later
on a school camping trip.

61
00:03:39,886 --> 00:03:43,932
In a tent, in the rain.
With his best friend, Chad.

62
00:03:45,266 --> 00:03:46,935
-Chad?
-I know.

63
