158
00:08:52,490 --> 00:08:55,326
You two seemed pretty copacetic,
sort of...

159
00:08:56,077 --> 00:08:58,663
Things were Ross and Rachel
with you and Renaldo.

160
00:08:59,497 --> 00:09:02,041
Yeah, I guess they were.

161
00:09:04,585 --> 00:09:05,670
Until they weren't.

162
00:09:05,753 --> 00:09:08,839
See, I thought I'd eliminated
all the obstacles between us, Beck.

163
00:09:08,923 --> 00:09:13,094
Benji. Peach.
But now, another has reared its head.

164
00:09:13,177 --> 00:09:14,887
And he's sitting right in front of me.

165
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:23,271
All right, Paul,
let's keep digging into this.

166
00:09:23,354 --> 00:09:26,732
All right, tell me, when did you see
the first cracks with Renaldo?

167
00:09:30,945 --> 00:09:33,239
Well, having Renaldo at work
was amazing,

168
00:09:33,906 --> 00:09:35,866
